<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-57-0470 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper provides a summary of developments in solar energy technology.It discusses biomass production for synthetic fuels like ethanol; buildingenergy systems using solar hot water systems; solar thermal energy systemsdesigned to convert solar radiation to heat for industrial or chemicalprocesses or to generate electricity; photovoltaics; ocean thermal energyconversion; and wind. The development of new materials and collectorsis discussed along with their application.</TEXT></DOC>